WEBVTT

00:00.333 --> 00:01.867
 Please, don't try anything

00:01.867 --> 00:03.902
 that you're about to see us do
 at home.

00:03.903 --> 00:06.903
 Ever!

00:08.074 --> 00:10.442
 NARRATOR: On this episode
 of "Mythbusters"...

00:10.443 --> 00:12.244
 Ba-da-da-da!
 Ba-da-da! 

00:12.245 --> 00:15.245
 NARRATOR:... Doctors Hyneman
 and Savage raid the "Ark"-hives

00:16.315 --> 00:19.316
 for a movie myth
 about a bike flip.

00:19.652 --> 00:21.053
 [ Laughter ]

00:21.054 --> 00:23.555
 If you poke a pole
 in the front spokes,

00:23.556 --> 00:26.158
 will it really flip out?

00:26.159 --> 00:27.192
 [ Laughter ]

00:27.193 --> 00:28.727
 The timing was perfect.

00:28.728 --> 00:30.996
 -lf you say so, Junior.
 -[ Laughs ]

00:30.997 --> 00:33.997
 NARRATOR: And Kari, Grant,
 and Tory are breaking bad...

00:34.067 --> 00:35.834
 I'm bustin' out of here, see?

00:35.835 --> 00:38.835
 NARRATOR:... to test tall tales
 of prison breaks.

00:39.272 --> 00:41.673
 They want to know
 if you can rappel to freedom

00:41.674 --> 00:44.674
 using bedsheets, toilet paper...

00:44.711 --> 00:46.045
 Freedom!

00:46.046 --> 00:47.513
 -NARRATOR:... and hair?
 -[Bleep]

00:47.514 --> 00:50.514
 -Oh! Oh!
 -Ow!

00:54.587 --> 00:57.289
 NARRATOR:
 Who are the Mythbusters?

00:57.290 --> 00:58.557
 Adam Savage...

00:58.558 --> 01:00.759
 That's 100 % wacky right there.

01:00.760 --> 01:03.328
 -NARRATOR:... and Jamie Hyneman.
 -Pain is your friend.

01:03.329 --> 01:05.197
 NARRATOR:
 Between them, more than 30 years

01:05.197 --> 01:07.733
 of special-effects experience.

01:07.734 --> 01:10.734
 Joining them -- Kari Byron...

01:11.438 --> 01:13.205
 -Let's do it.
 -NARRATOR:... Grant Imahara...

01:13.206 --> 01:15.240
 Danger!
 Warning! Warning!

01:15.241 --> 01:16.909
 NARRATOR:
...and Tory Belleci.

01:16.910 --> 01:19.211
 Okay, you want to play rough,
 little gopher?

01:19.212 --> 01:21.947
 NARRATOR:
 They don't just tell the myths.

01:21.948 --> 01:24.948
 They put them to the test.

